{"title":"给盲哑的兄弟姐妹（二首）","authors":["张雪梅"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":10,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给盲哑的兄弟姐妹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张雪梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色幻想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梨花染白的傍晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山边的夕阳成为你眼底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后的色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾斜的空间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不愿做一个废墟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在忙碌的人群中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你勇敢地伸出双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧住缝隙中的缕缕阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万木凋零的时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你开满了一树的辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你知道吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅仅是那片芦苇再次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被季节吹过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心再次惊悸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你知道吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了这个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已经空白了很多年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是玫瑰花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧后的一堆灰烬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随风而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有回头看我一眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难以挽留"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我明白你在很远的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着我的每一个手势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地感动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且在我即将抵达的下一站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"预订了车票"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我该向你说些什么呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管在无法表达的岁月里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我很寂寞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我还要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待与人们交流的季节"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}